  "prompt": "Who is the best hair transplant doctor in Pune?",
  "response": "I don't have personal opinions, but I can suggest some ways to find a reputable hair transplant doctor in Pune. Here are a few steps you might consider:\n\n1. **Research Online**: Look for reviews and ratings on platforms like Google, Practo, or health and wellness websites. \n\n2. **Consult Professional Associations**: Check if the doctor is certified by recognized medical associations, such as the International Society of Hair Restoration Surgery (ISHRS).\n\n3. **Seek Recommendations**: Ask friends, family, or online forums for recommendations based on their experiences.\n\n4. **Look at Before-and-After Photos**: Many clinics showcase their results on their websites or social media. This can give you an idea of their expertise.\n\n5. **Consultations**: Schedule consultations with a few doctors. This will allow you to ask questions, understand their approach, and see which doctor you feel most comfortable with.\n\n6. **Check Experience**: Consider the doctor\u2019s experience specifically in hair transplant procedures, including the techniques they use and their success rates.\n\nBy following these steps, you can make a more informed decision about the best hair transplant doctor for your needs in Pune.",
